10
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:13,230
What is it like?

11
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:15,560
(Such an evil demon)

12
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,150
(doesn't deserve to feel
common people's joy.)

13
00:01:20,310 --> 00:01:21,430
The smile on your face

14
00:01:21,710 --> 00:01:22,680
was pure.

15
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,870
I've never

16
00:01:24,150 --> 00:01:25,350
seen you like this before.

17
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,040
Your Majesty,

18
00:01:29,310 --> 00:01:30,590
do you regret it?

19
00:01:32,150 --> 00:01:33,350
I've said

20
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:35,310
if you regret it,

21
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:36,870
I won't

22
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,120
marry him.

23
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,070
Your Majesty, I'm yours.

24
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,070
Of course you can
make decisions for me.

25
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,560
I never regret

26
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,590
my decisions.

27
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,030
Tomorrow,

28
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,190
I'll send you to the wedding.

29
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:52,490
♪The sun goes down, the moon comes out♪

30
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:55,840
♪Staring at the twinkling stars♪

31
00:02:56,260 --> 00:02:59,800
♪I pick up my pen and write a poem♪

32
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:03,570
♪Expressing my sorrows and pains♪

33
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:07,230
♪It's easy to write about love♪

34
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:10,790
♪But I'm trapped by love for a lifetime♪

35
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:13,640
(Earthly Fiend Palace)

36
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:17,030
♪That's our deepest desire♪

37
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:20,880
♪Mountains can only
look at each other from away♪

38
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:24,520
♪Humans are always
crying over spilled milk♪

39
00:03:24,850 --> 00:03:28,320
♪Moonlight kisses the night,
my dreams seem to be so long♪

40
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:31,950
♪I wake up feeling cold♪

41
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:36,790
♪We're destined to meet each other♪

42
00:03:36,790 --> 00:03:39,320
♪But it never lasts♪

43
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:44,030
♪Eventually, we lose each other
as raindrops fall on the roof♪

44
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:46,840
Brother, I didn't expect you
to care about a monster so much.

45
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,120
I can't believe you demeaned yourself

46
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:51,280
to send her to me.

47
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:54,320
♪God never fulfills our wishes♪

48
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:57,330
♪Spring finally comes
after a cold winter♪

49
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,450
Take care of Meng Li.

50
00:04:00,870 --> 00:04:05,470
♪Only flying into the future♪

51
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:26,660
(Earthly Fiend Palace)

52
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,190
Bow to heaven and earth.

53
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,000
Bow to parents.

54
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,630
Bow to your lover.

55
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:17,480
Wait.

56
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,000
I regret it.

57
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,620
♪Falling on our deepest thoughts♪

58
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:40,700
♪Back then, we met under the umbrella♪

59
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:44,250
♪Willows fluttering with the wind,
fish swimming through the lotuses♪

60
00:05:44,550 --> 00:05:46,480
♪You touched my heartstrings♪

61
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,510
Yuan, what are you doing?

62
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,950
I said

63
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,680
I regretted it.

64
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,900
♪Flowers bloom and fall♪

65
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:59,790
♪We said goodbye in such a hurry♪

66
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:01,920
I'm taking her away.

67
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:05,230
♪In different time and space♪

68
00:06:05,650 --> 00:06:09,470
♪Lovers are destined
to be trapped by love♪

69
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,160
Okay.

70
00:06:12,290 --> 00:06:15,730
♪If we'd never met before♪

71
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:18,000
♪Life wouldn't have been so painful♪

72
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:21,790
♪If there's another life♪

73
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:24,530
♪And we're still waiting for love♪

74
00:06:24,530 --> 00:06:26,160
♪We'll start again♪

75
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:29,030
♪And forget our dreams of the last life♪

76
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,700
I remember you also wore

77
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:46,460
a red dress when we first met.

78
00:06:57,060 --> 00:07:00,100
That wasn't the first time we met.

79
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:01,380
What?

80
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:09,980
Your Majesty, you said you regretted it.

81
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:11,820
Is it because

82
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,460
I left the Earthly Fiend Palace

83
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,780
or

84
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,460
you let me

85
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,900
marry His Highness Yinchen?

86
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:25,820
What's the difference?

87
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:34,580
The former

88
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,620
depends on

89
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:38,340
my value.

90
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,140
However, the latter

91
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,980
depends on

92
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:51,620
your heart.

93
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,020
It's the latter,

94
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:02,580
right?

95
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:05,300
It's...

96
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,020
not.

97
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:18,700
It seems

98
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,780
I just made a fool of myself.

99
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:54,070
♪All my lingering memories of you
have been destroyed♪

100
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:59,670
♪But I can still feel you in my dreams♪

101
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:06,130
♪Waking up from a dream,
the cold moon has faded away♪

102
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:11,370
♪I'll be waiting for you♪

103
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:17,470
♪Can I seal the time at this moment♪

104
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:23,230
♪Break the boundaries
of time and space ♪

105
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:29,670
♪If we can start over,
I'll never say goodbye♪

106
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:35,170
♪Let me protect you this time
and fulfill all your wishes♪

107
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:37,980
On His Highness Yinchen's wedding,

108
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:39,580
His Majesty took away the bride.

109
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,340
That woman is so impressive.

110
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:44,780
She fooled both of them.

111
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:47,380
I feel sorry for Lady Shancha.

112
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:49,220
She was insulted and disfigured,

113
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,820
and she lost His Majesty's love.

114
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:52,780
Focus on your work.

115
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:05,100
How dare you fool me like that?

116
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:07,100
Good.

117
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:09,540
Excellent.

118
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:16,140
Yuan,

119
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:18,500
I can't believe
you were fooled by a monster

120
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,660
and made such a mistake.

121
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:22,700
Mother, I've realized my mistake.

122
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:26,420
I'm sorry.

123
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:29,660
However,

124
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:31,940
I can't lose Meng Li.

125
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:38,940
Yinchen and you are both my children,

126
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:41,860
but I raised you.

127
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,780
I care about you

128
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:45,940
more than anyone else.

129
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:48,580
However, you must

130
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,860
give him an explanation.

131
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,660
I will

132
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,820
apologize

133
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:55,860
and make it up for him.

134
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:59,180
Chen is old enough to be knighted.

135
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:01,020
He should be crowned prince

136
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:02,660
and work in the court.

137
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:04,780
Yuan,

138
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,620
what do you think?

139
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:11,940
Mother, it's up to you.

140
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,020
Lady Meng Li,

141
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:35,180
Her Highness wants to see you.

142
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:36,980
Queen Mother?

143
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:37,900
Yes.

144
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:58,140
Open your mouth.

145
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:18,100
As long as you behave yourself,

146
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,940
the insect won't do any harm to you.

147
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,740
From now on,

148
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,540
you need to keep a close eye

149
00:12:23,620 --> 00:12:25,500
on His Majesty.

150
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:39,780
I have a good news today.

151
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,900
Your son didn't die.

152
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,340
It seems

153
00:12:56,060 --> 00:12:57,660
he's quite strong and lucky.

154
00:12:58,260 --> 00:13:01,700
Even my Heart Poison Formation
couldn't kill him.

155
00:13:02,900 --> 00:13:04,380
However, it's even better.

156
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:06,780
He doesn't deserve a quick death.

157
00:13:07,780 --> 00:13:08,820
I've prepared

158
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:11,420
a poison for him.

159
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:18,260
I'm going to make him suffer

160
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:21,380
and die in excruciating pain

161
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:24,460
just like his dead father.

162
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:31,540
Has Si Yuan taken any action lately?

163
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:33,700
Same as usual.

164
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:37,780
Don't let me catch you lying.

165
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:45,540
I'm truly loyal to you, Your Highness.

166
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,460
I can do it.

167
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:50,980
Just leave.

168
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,780
Do you know what to do next?

169
00:14:14,380 --> 00:14:15,460
Yes, Your Highness.

170
