177
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:55,670
♪It has nothing to do♪

178
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:57,670
♪With the vows we took♪

179
00:14:57,670 --> 00:15:00,870
♪Life is too difficult♪

180
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:02,270
